{"title":"22【练习】经典递归问题","slug":"22【练习】经典递归问题","date":"2018-10-26T08:50:45.000Z","updated":"2018-10-27T14:10:00.768Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/22【练习】经典递归问题.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"前言7个经典递归问题练习。","covers":null,"content":"<link rel=\"stylesheet\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-style-marker\" href=\"/assets/css/APlayer.min.css\"><script src=\"/assets/js/APlayer.min.js\" class=\"aplayer-secondary-script-marker\"></script><h2 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h2><p>7个经典递归问题练习。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"正文\"><a href=\"#正文\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"正文\"></a>正文</h2><ol>\n<li><p>在n个球中，任意取m个(不放回)，求有多少种取法</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int f(int n, int m)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if (n&lt;m)    // 3个球取4个出来 显然是0种取法</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        return 0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if (m==0)   // 3个球取0个出来 有1种取法</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        return 1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if (n==m)   // 3个球取3个出来 有1种取法</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        return 1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    return f(n-1, m-1) + f(n-1, m);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int main(int argc, const char * argv[])</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    int k = f(5, 3);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    printf(&quot;%d\\n&quot;, k);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    return 0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>求n个元素的全排列</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// abc acb bac bca cab cba</span><br><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">void f(char data[], int length, int cur)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tif(cur==length)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tprintf(&quot;%s\\n&quot;, data);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfor(int i=cur; i&lt;length; i++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#123;\t// 试探</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tchar tmp = data[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tdata[i] = data[cur];</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tdata[cur] = tmp;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tf(data, length, cur+1);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#123;\t// 回溯</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tchar tmp = data[i];</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tdata[i] = data[cur];</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tdata[cur] = tmp;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int main()</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tchar data[] = &quot;abcd&quot;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tint length = sizeof(data)/sizeof(data[0]) - 1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t//printf(&quot;%d\\n&quot;,length);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tf(data, length, 0);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\treturn 0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>两个串的最大公共子序列的长度</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// 可解!</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;string.h&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int MAX(int a, int b)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    return a&gt;b?a:b;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int f(char *s1, char *s2)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if (strlen(s1)*strlen(s2) == 0)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        return 0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if (s1[0] == s2[0])</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        return f(s1+1, s2+1) + 1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    else</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        return MAX(f(s1+1, s2), f(s1, s2+1));</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int main(int argc, const char * argv[])</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    char *s1 = &quot;abc&quot;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    char *s2 = &quot;xbacd&quot;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    int ret = f(s1, s2);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    printf(&quot;%d\\n&quot;, ret);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    return 0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>字符串反转</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 反转串</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 例如：abc  -&gt;  cba</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;string.h&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">void ReverseString(char *p)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    int length = strlen(p);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if(length &lt;= 1)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        return;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    else</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        char tmp = p[0];</span><br><span class=\"line\">        p[0] = p[length-1];</span><br><span class=\"line\">        p[length-1] = &apos;\\0&apos;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        ReverseString(p+1);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        p[length-1] = tmp;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int main()</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tchar p[] = &quot;abcd&quot;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ReverseString(p);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    printf(&quot;%s\\n&quot;, p);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\treturn 0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>组合问题</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 组合问题</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 3个A 2个B可以组成多少 种 排列</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 如：AAABB AABBA等</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// m个A n个B</span><br><span class=\"line\">int f(int m, int n)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if(m == 0 || n == 0)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        return 1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    // 假设首位置为A，则剩下m-1个A和n个B的组合问题 + 首位置为B...</span><br><span class=\"line\">    return f(m-1, n) + f(m, n-1);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int main()</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    printf(&quot;%d\\n&quot;, f(3, 1));</span><br><span class=\"line\">    return 0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>杨辉三角</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 杨辉三角</span><br><span class=\"line\">// 计算第m层第n个元素</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">/*</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 1</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 1 1</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 1 2 1</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 1 3 3 1</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 1 4 6 4 1</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 1 5 10 10 5 1</span><br><span class=\"line\"> */</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int f(int m, int n)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if(n == 0)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        return 1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if(m == n)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        return 1;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    return f(m-1, n) + f(m-1, n-1);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int main()</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    int leval = 5;  // 第5行 0-5共6个元素</span><br><span class=\"line\">    for(int i=0; i&lt;=leval; i++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        printf(&quot;%d &quot;, f(leval, i));</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    printf(&quot;\\n&quot;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    return 0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>整数划分问题</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">// 整数划分问题</span><br><span class=\"line\">// n = 6</span><br><span class=\"line\">/*</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 6</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 5+1</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 4+2,4+1+1</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 3+3,3+2+1,3+1+1+1</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 2+2+2,2+2+1+1,2+1+1+1+1</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 1+1+1+1+1+1</span><br><span class=\"line\"> */</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">#define MAXSIZE 1024</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">// arr-&gt;缓冲，cur-&gt;当前位置</span><br><span class=\"line\">void f(int n, int arr[], int cur)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if(n&lt;=0)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        for(int i=0; i&lt;cur; i++)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            printf(&quot;%d &quot;, arr[i]);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        printf(&quot;\\n&quot;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        return;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    for(int i=n; i&gt;0; i--)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        if(cur&gt;0 &amp;&amp; i&gt;arr[cur-1])</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            continue;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        arr[cur] = i;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        f(n-i, arr, cur+1);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">int main()</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    int arr[MAXSIZE] = &#123;0&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    f(6, arr, 0);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    return 0;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":[{"name":"练习","slug":"练习","count":9,"path":"api/categories/练习.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"练习","slug":"练习","count":10,"path":"api/tags/练习.json"},{"name":"递归","slug":"递归","count":1,"path":"api/tags/递归.json"},{"name":"算法","slug":"算法","count":2,"path":"api/tags/算法.json"}]}